                                            HTML


HTML is not a programming language(no loops, no variables etc), it is a markup language.

Basic HTML Program:


<!DOCTYPE html>  // Document type declaration

<html lang="en"> // open tag/ start tag ; lang = "en" -> attribute en - english
    <head> // open heading tag
        <title> // open title tag
            hello, title 
        </title> // close title tag

    </head> // close heading tag
    <body>  // open body tag
        hello, body 
    </body>  // close body tag
</html> // close tag/ end tag
    

* phishing
* #- unique identifier
* . - class centered

